title: What are your favorite qualities about yourself? :)
body:
Hello all~

I haven't been posting as much lately, so I figured it's about time I bug y'all some more :3

What are some things you like about yourself and if there isn't really anything worth saying then what are the kind of qualities you enjoy in people?

So, for me I like my ability to stay positive and happy even during bad days and I'm quick to feel better when I'm down, and I love the way I look. :) 

... Go! 

O u O
